---
// BaseLayout can't be rendered live inside the styleguide [slug] page
// (that would produce nested <html> documents). This static preview
// describes the layout's shape, slots, and the meta tags it emits.
---

<div class="space-y-6">
  <section>
    <h3 class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-ink-3);">Shape</h3>
    <pre
      class="mt-2"
      style="background: var(--color-ink); color: var(--color-bg); padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap;"
    >
{`<!doctype html>
<html lang="en-AU">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="..." />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{description}" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="{canonical}" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="{title}" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="{description}" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="{canonical}" />
    {ogImage && <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />}
    {noIndex && <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />}
    <slot name="schema" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <slot />
  </body>
</html>`}
    </pre>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3 class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-ink-3);">
      Slots
    </h3>
    <ul
      class="mt-3 space-y-0"
      style="border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); background: var(--color-bg);"
    >
      <li
        class="flex gap-3 px-5 py-3"
        style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);"
      >
        <code class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-accent); min-width: 6rem;">schema</code>
        <span class="t-body" style="color: var(--color-ink-2); font-size: 14px;">
          Where the archetype layout injects its JSON-LD via
          <code>set:html=&#123;JSON.stringify(graph)&#125;</code>.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 px-5 py-3">
        <code class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-accent); min-width: 6rem;">(default)</code>
        <span class="t-body" style="color: var(--color-ink-2); font-size: 14px;">
          Page body. Archetype layouts compose sections here.
        </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3 class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-ink-3);">
      Composition pattern
    </h3>
    <p class="t-body mt-2" style="color: var(--color-ink-2); font-size: 14px; max-width: 75ch;">
      Archetype layouts wrap BaseLayout. A
      <code>CoursePageLayout.astro</code> would receive the page frontmatter,
      call <code>buildCourseGraph(frontmatter, faqs)</code>, and pass both the
      schema JSON-LD and the composed sections through to BaseLayout's slots.
    </p>
  </section>
</div>
